{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"scalesWithViewingDistance"}],"title":"scalesWithViewingDistance","fragments":[{"text":"scalesWithViewingDistance","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L180","fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h"},"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)scalesWithViewingDistance","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view grows and shrinks","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as the distance between the viewpoint and the annotation view changes on a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tilted map.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"scalesWithViewingDistance"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and the map is tilted, the annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view appears smaller if it is towards the top of the view (closer to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"horizon) and larger if it is towards the bottom of the view (closer to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"viewpoint). This is also the behavior of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" objects. When the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or the map’s pitch is zero, the annotation view","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"remains the same size regardless of its position on-screen.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":". Keep this property set to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":" if"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the view’s legibility is important."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Note","style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Scaling many on-screen annotation views can contribute to poor map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"performance. Consider keeping this property disabled if your use case","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"involves hundreds or thousands of annotation views.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/scalesWithViewingDistance","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","title":"MLNAnnotationView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView",